name: body
description: The container for a web page's content. Must be a direct child of <html>, and must be an ancestor of all HTML elements (except where noted).

name: br
description: Defines a line break within a text.

name: b
description: Makes an element bold.

name: bdo
description: Allows to override the direction of text.

name: caption
description: Defines the title of a <table>.

name: col
description: Defines a column within a table.

name: code
description: Defines a snippet of code within a block of text.

name: address
description: Defines a block for contact information.

name: base
description: Defines the base URL for all relative links of a web page. Should be placed in the <head>.

name: abbr
description: Defines an abbreviation, and usually includes its full description.

name: blockquote
description: Defines a long quotation.

name: dl
description: Defines a definition list.

name: em
description: Defines emphasis on text. Is usually rendered as italic text.

name: dd
description: Defines an item in a definition list.

name: article
description: Defines a self-contained block of content that can exist in any context.It can have its own header, footer, sections... Useful for a list of blog posts.

name: audio
description: Allows to embed an audio clip into a web page.

name: data
description: Defines content linked to machine-readable output.

name: aside
description: Defines a block of content that is related to the main content. Displayed as a sidebar usually.

name: dialog
description: Defines a dialog box that can be opened and closed with JavaScript.

name: bdi
description: Allows to display part of a text in the opposite direction. Stands for bidirectional isolation.

name: h1
description: Defines a section heading of level one: the highest level.

name: dt
description: Defines a definition term.

name: h2
description: Defines a section heading of level two.

name: footer
description: Defines the footer of a web page or section.

name: del
description: Defines text that has been deleted.

name: datalist
description: Defines a list of autocomplete options when using a text <input>.

name: figure
description: Defines a single self-contained element, usually an image.

name: button
description: Defines a clickable button.

name: iframe
description: Defines a container for a nested browsing context: you can include a web page within another web page.

name: dfn
description: Defines where a term is defined within a web page.

name: figcaption
description: Defines the caption of a <figure>.

name: h5
description: Defines a section heading of level five.

name: ol
description: Defines an ordered list.

name: hr
description: Defines a semantic break between blocks of text. It is often represented as a horizontal rule.

name: h3
description: Defines a section heading of level three.

name: h6
description: Defines a section heading of level six: the lowest level.

name: hgroup
description: Defines the heading of a section. It can only contain heading levels: <h1> <h2> <h3> <h4> <h5> <h6>

name: a
description: Creates a link to a URL: a web page, a section within a page, an email address... Also called the anchor element, where the a comes from.

name: canvas
description: Defines an element where you can draw graphics.

name: li
description: Defines a list item within an ordered list <ol> or unordered list <ul>.

name: header
description: Defines the header of a web page or section.

name: i
description: Makes an element italic.

name: label
description: Defines a label for a form control.

name: ins
description: Defines text that has been inserted.

name: main
description: Defines the main content of a web page. Can be displayed with a sidebar.

name: rp
description: Defines content displayed when the browser does not support the <ruby> element.

name: q
description: Defines a short quotation.

name: strong
description: Defines strong importance on text.

name: ruby
description: Defines a ruby annotation to show the pronunciation of East Asian characters.

name: progress
description: Defines a progress bar.

name: colgroup
description: Defines a group of columns within a table.

name: cite
description: Defines the source of a creative work.

name: fieldset
description: Defines a group of controls within a form.

name: div
description: Defines a generic block of content, that does not carry any semantic value. Used for layout elements like containers.

name: head
description: Defines a container for a web page's metadata.

name: embed
description: Defines a container for external application.

name: h4
description: Defines a section heading of level four.

name: img
description: Defines an image inserted in the web page.

name: option
description: Defines an option within a <select> dropdown.

name: noframes
description: Defines content displayed when the browser does not support frames.

name: picture
description: Defines a container for sources of an element.

name: kbd
description: Defines a snippet of user input.

name: mark
description: Defines highlighted text.

name: s
description: Defines strikethrough text.

name: map
description: Defines an interactive map over an image.

name: legend
description: Defines a caption for a parent's content.

name: noscript
description: Defines content displayed when the browser does not have JavaScript enabled.

name: title
description: Defines the title of the web page, displayed on the browser tab.

name: wbr
description: Defines a location within a block of text where the browser could eventually insert line break.

name: area
description: Defines an interactive area within a map.

name: template
description: Defines a placeholder for content that can be displayed using JavaScript.

name: form
description: Defines an interactive form with controls.

name: output
description: Defines the result of a calculation or of user action.

name: link
description: Defines a link between the current web page and an external link or resource.

name: nav
description: Defines a section with navigation links.

name: p
description: Defines a simple paragraph of text.

name: script
description: Defines a container for an external script.

name: select
description: Defines a select dropdown with different <option> elements.

name: input
description: Defines an interactive control within a web form.

name: ul
description: Defines an unordered list.

name: object
description: Defines a container for external resource.

name: sub
description: Defines text that should be displayed lower.

name: textarea
description: Defines a multi-line text control within a web form.

name: td
description: Defines a table cell.

name: track
description: Defines text tracks (like subtitles) for <audio> and <video> elements.

name: u
description: Makes an element's text underlined.

name: thead
description: Defines a group of table rows <tr> at the start of a <table>.

name: meta
description: Defines metadata attached to a web page.

name: sup
description: Defines text that should be displayed higher.

name: section
description: Defines a section within a web page.

name: tbody
description: Defines a group of table rows <tr>.

name: rtc
description: Defines a text container within ruby annotations.

name: span
description: Defines a generic inline container of content, that does not carry any semantic value.

name: slot
description: Defines a container for user markup.

name: table
description: Defines a container for tabular data.

name: style
description: Defines a container to add CSS within a web page.

name: rt
description: Defines the pronunciation of ruby annotations.

name: small
description: Defines small print, for less important content.

name: samp
description: Defines a sample output from a computer program.

name: pre
description: Defines preformatted text.

name: summary
description: Defines the summary of a <details> element.

name: video
description: Allows to embed an video clip into a web page.

name: var
description: Defines a variable in a mathematical or programming expression.

name: source
description: Defines a source for an <audio>, <video>, or <picture> element.

name: meter
description: Defines a horizontal meter.

name: param
description: Defines a parameter for an <object> element.

name: optgroup
description: Defines a group of <option> elements.

name: th
description: Defines a table header.

name: time
description: Defines a time on a 24h clock.

name: tfoot
description: Defines a group of table rows <tr> at the end of a <table>.

name: tr
description: Defines a table row.

name: html
description: Defines the root element of an HTML document. All other elements must be contained within this root element.

name: details
description: Defines a toggable block of content with a summary and additional details.
